The paper proposes a method for estimating the trajectory of a flying object using ground cameras, which involves computer vision and robotics. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves optimization and regularization techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.CVPR (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Finally, the paper deals with the flight dynamics of the UAV, which could be relevant to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
